lead_paragraph: Rich Barcelo shot an eight-under 64 yesterday at PGA West in La Quinta, Calif., to take a three-stroke lead over Australia’s Paul Gow after the second round of the PGA Tour’s 108-hole final qualifying tournament. Barcelo, who has reached the PGA Tour only once in eight previous qualifying tries, had a nine-under 135.
